data.description: The beautiful home in The Groves has been well maintained and very spacious. It comes with 4 bedrooms and 3.5 bathrooms. It has over $100,000 in upgrades from double ovens, Tile throughout home, double doors on front entrance, high ceilings, quartz countertops in kitchen and bathrooms, upgraded pad under carpet, Vacuum in the walls that empties out in the garage, wiring for cable in the walls and extended patio. Surround sound in living room, game room and patio. Sub roofer will stay with home. Ceiling fans where added on patio as well. 3 panel door open to patio that makes for great entertainment. Blinds throughout home. Walk in pantry and 3 car garage. Office in front with a ceiling fan. All rooms cable access. Seller is leaving two ceiling fans that where bought for the house as well. Come out and see what this house has to offer.
